      "code": "def search_in_hadith(query_norm):\n    res = []\n    for h in hadith:\n        text = h.get('hadithTxt') or h.get('Matn') or ''\n        norm = normalize_ar(text)\n        if query_norm in norm:\n            res.append(h)\n    return res\n\nmatches = search_in_hadith(norm_target)\nlen(matches)",
      "container_id": "cntr_689672790eec8190a4f61362d20fac8804b2fdab08686391",
