      "code": "# Maybe the hadith text stored in Matn field instead; check both\ndef search_any(term):\n    qn = normalize_ar(term)\n    out = []\n    for h in hadith:\n        for field in ('hadithTxt','Matn'):\n            text = h.get(field) or ''\n            if qn in normalize_ar(text):\n                out.append((h['hadithID'], field, text[:120]))\n                break\n    return out\n\nsearch_any(\"اقرءوا القران\"), len(search_any(\"اقرءوا القران\"))",
